### --- ORGANIZATION (Location & Sites) ---

### Criar Location
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organization/locations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Matriz Joinville",
  "address": "Rua Dona Francisca, 8300"
}

### Listar Locations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organization/locations

### Criar Site (Vinculado a Location 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organization/sites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Data Center Principal",
  "location": { "id": 1 }
}

### Listar Sites
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organization/sites


### --- INFRASTRUCTURE (Racks) ---

### Criar Rack (Vinculado ao Site 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/racks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rack Servidores A",
  "uHeight": 42,
  "site": { "id": 1 }
}

### Listar Racks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/racks


