### --- NOVOS TESTES DE IPAM (Redes e IPs) ---

### 1. Criar Rede (Prefixo)
# Vinculada ao Site 1 e VLAN 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ipam/prefixes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cidr": "192.168.10.0/24",
  "name": "Rede Dados Escritorio",
  "site": { "id": 1 },
  "vlan": { "id": 1 }
}

### 2. Listar Redes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ipam/prefixes

### 3. Criar Endere√ßo IP
# Vinculado ao Dispositivo 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ipam/ip-addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "192.168.10.1/24",
  "status": "Active",
  "dnsName": "gw-switch-core.local",
  "device": { "id": 1 }
}

### 4. Listar IPs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ipam/ip-addresses

### 5. Atualizar IP (Mudar status)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/ipam/ip-addresses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "192.168.10.1/24",
  "status": "Reserved",
  "dnsName": "gw-switch-core.local",
  "device": { "id": 1 }
}

### 6. Excluir IP
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ipam/ip-addresses/1